Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間桐慎二 我的代理Master
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間桐櫻的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如您所見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個冷靜沉著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眉清目秀的大好青年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美到讓我感覺配不上他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利刷新記錄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有我在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可氣的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵沒法選擇長官
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起一味抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是去發掘他的長處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你不一樣 對那種無聊的雜務沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 那也要有得發掘才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼豐富多彩的校園生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這多半是常人無法想像的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才獨有的扭曲性格所造成的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.44,0:00:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連他不經意間的一舉一動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都惹我討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 你還在啊 衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 叫住朋友時還蠻可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算是他為數不多的長處之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 拍學生會的馬屁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這段精彩絕倫的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一筆勾銷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用掉真的好嗎 衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.73,0:01:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是慎二嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自曝身份的 勇敢的麻煩鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說Saber的Master夠外行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.49,0:01:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的Master也不落下風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛宮已經有兩年沒來過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 她要在一旁陪著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也害怕你的Servant嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你也把Servant叫出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕 有你一個威懾力就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 沒用的傢伙 還是老樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾秒鐘 我的手險些就要滑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算和半吊子Master合作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說我已經有衛宮同學做搭檔了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他比你可靠得多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛宮和你？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜 打得不夠狠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠遠不夠…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你比想像中的有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是使用我的寶具之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鮮血神殿的戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 他也揭示了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「求人怎能不下跪」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一無比精闢的人生觀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這命令口氣不太對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想求我住手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就該跪下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求人怎能不下跪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就交給你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發覺勢頭不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上腳底抹油的英明判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩服佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rider 你搞什麼呢Rider！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎二！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 一定要由我親手結果他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 是我錯了 衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就解開結界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rider！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開鮮血神殿 馬上！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道會落得這種下場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部 全部 全部 全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部殺掉 全部破壞掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎二這孩子  真讓人頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提 我的寶具不是天馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是韁繩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它被冠以希臘神話裡馴服天馬的英雄之名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？ 慎二？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:04:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該退場了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是Saber礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能連他一起來個痛快的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 我和他的戲份結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 退場方式還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡有惡報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家也多多注意平日的言行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了交到一個好女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力吧